---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use" description="DataIsland Software Terms of Use">

  <section class="legal fade-in">
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>

    <p>
      By using DataIsland Software products and services, you agree to the following terms.
      These terms ensure a safe, predictable, and privacy‑respecting experience for all users.
    </p>

    <h2>Use of Applications</h2>
    <p>
      DataIsland applications are provided "as‑is" without warranties of any kind. You are
      responsible for ensuring that your use complies with local laws and regulations.
    </p>

    <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>
      All software, branding, and content produced by DataIsland Software is protected by
      copyright and may not be redistributed, modified, or resold without permission.
    </p>

    <h2>Acceptable Use</h2>
    <p>
      You agree not to misuse our applications, attempt unauthorized access, or interfere
      with the normal operation of our services or infrastructure.
    </p>

    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>
      DataIsland Software is not liable for any damages arising from the use or inability
      to use our applications, including data loss or service interruptions.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p>
      We may update these terms periodically. Continued use of our products constitutes
      acceptance of the updated terms.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For questions regarding these terms, contact:
      <br />
      <strong>support@dataisland.com</strong>
    </p>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .legal h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .legal h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
</style>
